{
  "stem": "16345.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, there was a blizzard in New York at the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed at a-- a-- a sort of a charity children's home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at-- at the time I was beginning to learn some English, like, and I wanted-- I wanted some American food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Didn't have much money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did have two granduncles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My grandmoth-- my grandmother had two brothers who were up in-- in-- in their 60s who lived in New York.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they want-- actually wanted me to stay with them, but I decided no.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wanted to see the country, and I wanted to see the world.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't want to interrupt their lives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at the time I also realized that people-- Jewish people in this country-- really didn't know what had been going on in Europe.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was once among a group of them, and we-- we were having dinner or something, and they started asking me questions.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I actually-- I actually started telling them the way things really were, and they looked at me as if I was telling them stories that I had just made up on the spur of the moment.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's when I decided--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It did-- it didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was indignant, but I kept quiet about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned to mask my feelings at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's understandable that-- that they didn't believe me, because who could believe anything like that?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's when I decided I was going to keep my mouth shut until necessary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when somebody asked me, well, how-- everybody wanted to know-- well, how were things over there in concentration camp, I'd say oh, pretty bad, and that's all-- without details.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
